Implement SLDS Toast notifications on the Waivers component to display user feedback messages (Success, Info, Warning, and Error) following Salesforce Lightning Design System standards.

Currently, messages are not aligned with SLDS toast guidelines. This enhancement will standardize notifications using SLDS toast styling to improve user experience and maintain UI consistency.

1️⃣ Success Message

When an action completes successfully (e.g., save/update/submit):

A green Success toast is displayed.

Toast includes:

Success icon

Clear success message

Auto-dismiss behavior (if applicable)

2️⃣ Error Message

When an action fails (server-side or validation error):

A red Error toast is displayed.

Toast includes:

Error icon

Proper error message from Apex/validation

Toast does NOT show white background (must follow SLDS styling)

3️⃣ Warning Message

When a warning condition occurs:

A yellow Warning toast is displayed.

Appropriate warning icon is shown.

4️⃣ Info Message

Informational messages display:

Blue Info toast

Info icon

Clear message text
